Nithish M S

Clinical SAS Programmer | CDISC SDTM | ADaM | TLF Programming
⸻
Professional Summary

Motivated Clinical SAS Programmer with hands-on experience in developing CDISC-compliant SDTM and ADaM datasets, generating TLF outputs, and creating submission-ready XPT files using SAS 9.4. This portfolio demonstrates practical project work completed through independent learning, project development, and Clinical SAS training.

Core competencies include Clinical Data Mapping, SDTM Domain Development, ADaM Dataset Creation, TLF Programming, PROC SQL, PROC REPORT, PROC TRANSPOSE, PROC SUMMARY, Data Validation, and XPT Generation.
