Portfolio Projects

1. SDTM DM Domain Development

Objective

Transform raw demographic data into a CDISC SDTM-compliant DM dataset.

Key Features

* USUBJID derivation
* ISO8601 date conversion
* Subject demographic mapping
* SDTM variable labeling
* XPT generation

